skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: gloucester guide
des:
Welcome to the historic seaside city of Gloucester Massachusetts! This skill will be your local guide.

For suggestions on restaurants, just say "coffee", "breakfast", "lunch", or "dinner"; or ask "recommend an attraction" or just say "go outside" for the current weather conditions.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
